Package dataPlotsFX.data

Class TDDataListInfoFX

java.lang.Object
dataPlotsFX.data.TDDataListInfoFX
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
public class TDDataListInfoFX extends Object implements Serializable, Cloneable
TDDataInfo objects can't be serialised since they contain references back into datablocks and everything else in PAMguard, so have to hold a summary of what's in each one to save into psf files.
Author:
Doug Gillespie
